    "The specific model is as follows:",
    "where, Cer i,t represents the rating of green bond i by third parties in time t. If the green bond has no third-party rating, the value is 0.",
    "If the rating is AA -, the value is 1.",
    "If it is AA, the value is 2.",
    "If it is AA +, the value is 3."
  ],
